---
layout: vertical.njk
title: Prompts
pageTitle: Prompt library
pageSubtitle: Reusable prompts shared across the team. Click "Use" to send to the AI panel.
permalink: /ai/prompts/index.html
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "BX-AI+", href: "/" }
  - { label: "AI" }
  - { label: "Prompts" }
---

<div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center gap-2 mb-3">
  <div class="bx-ai-page__search" style="max-width:320px;flex:1;">
    <i data-lucide="search" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    <input type="search" placeholder="Search prompts…" aria-label="Search prompts">
  </div>
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">
    <i data-lucide="plus" style="width:14px;height:14px;"></i> New prompt
  </button>
</div>

<div class="bx-prompt-filters" data-bx-prompt-filters>
  {% for c in aiPrompts.categories %}
  <button type="button"
          data-bx-prompt-filter="{{ c.id }}"
          {% if c.id == "all" %}class="is-active"{% endif %}>
    {{ c.label }}
    <span class="bx-prompt-filters__count">{{ c.count }}</span>
  </button>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="row g-3" data-bx-prompt-grid>
  {% for p in aiPrompts.prompts %}
  <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4" data-bx-prompt-cat="{{ p.category }}">
    <div class="bx-prompt-card">
      <div class="bx-prompt-card__head">
        <h3 class="bx-prompt-card__title">{{ p.title }}</h3>
        <button type="button"
                class="bx-prompt-card__star {% if p.favorite %}is-on{% endif %}"
                aria-label="Toggle favorite"
                data-bx-prompt-star>
          <i data-lucide="star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
      <span class="bx-prompt-card__cat bx-prompt-card__cat--{{ p.tone }}">{{ p.categoryLabel }}</span>
      <p class="bx-prompt-card__snip">{{ p.snippet }}</p>
      <div class="bx-prompt-card__foot">
        <span class="bx-prompt-card__author">
          <i data-lucide="user" style="width:12px;height:12px;"></i>
          {{ p.author }} · {{ p.uses }} uses · {{ p.updated }}
        </span>
        <button type="button"
                class="bx-prompt-card__use bx-ai-ask-btn"
                data-bx-ai-ask
                data-ai-context="prompt-{{ p.id }}"
                data-ai-prompt="{{ p.snippet }}">
          <i data-lucide="play" aria-hidden="true"></i> Use
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
